			<td bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="/images/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				This area is like the warrior arenas in the various cities, except it's bigger.  If you step into the central part of the arena, you will become PvP and other players can kill you.  This effect goes away when you leave the central area.<BR>
<BR>
Outside of the central area is a normal zone where you are NOT PvP.  Even better, you can be bound to this zone as though it were a city.  This is a good idea if you want to hunt gnolls in Paw.<BR>
<BR>
No MOBs exist in this zone.  It's pretty boring, actually.<BR>

				</font>
